# Alerts Center — Implementation Plan

## Goal

Build the **Alerts Center** as a standalone case-centric signal hub at `/dashboard/alerts`. This replaces the current simple [AlertsList](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertsList.tsx#12-115)+[AlertDrawer](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertDrawer.tsx#16-146) with a full split-pane layout featuring: sticky filters, alert card list (left), details panel (right), bulk actions, CSV export, full lifecycle state machine, RBAC enforcement, audit logging, and keyboard shortcuts — all using **client-side data only** (no backend changes).

---

