## Role Mapping

The spec references roles not in code. Mapping:

| Spec Role | Code Role | Notes |
|-----------|-----------|-------|
| HR | `admin` | Full access |
| Dept Manager | `manager` | Department-scoped |
| Team Supervisor | `employee` | Team-scoped |
| Executive | *(simulated via filter)* | Aggregate-only view — enforced in UI |
| Data Analyst | *(simulated via filter)* | View-only, no actions |
| System Admin | `super_admin` | Data Quality only |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Since the project only has 4 roles (`admin`/`manager`/`employee`/`super_admin`), we map the 6 spec roles to these 4 and implement the closest permission set possible without inventing new roles.

