## Proposed Changes

### Types Layer

#### [NEW] [alerts.ts](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/types/alerts.ts)
All alert type contracts per spec: [AlertSeverity](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts#4-5), [AlertStatus](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts#5-6), `AlertType`, [Alert](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts#59-70), `AlertDetails`, `AlertDriver`, `AlertAuditEvent`, `AlertFilters`, and permission types.

---

### Data Layer

#### [MODIFY] [alert.store.ts](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts)
Complete rewrite:
- Expand [SystemAlert](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts#8-21) → new [Alert](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts#59-70) type from `types/alerts.ts`
- Add full lifecycle: `NEW → ACKNOWLEDGED → ACTIONED → CLOSED → ARCHIVED`
- Add audit trail (append-only log persisted to `alert_audit_v1`)
- Add ~15 diverse mock alerts across all 5 types
- Add actions: `acknowledge`, `assign`, `convertToCase`, [dismiss](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/hooks/use-toast.ts#150-151), `escalate`, [close](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/websocket.ts#33-39), `archive`, `markRead`, `markAllRead`, `bulkAcknowledge`, `bulkConvertToCase`
- Add `getAlertDetails(id)` returning `AlertDetails` with XAI explanation mocks
- Persist to `alerts_v1` localStorage key
- Keep backward compat: old `smart-hr-alerts-storage` key will be superseded

#### [NEW] [alerts.adapter.ts](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/adapters/alerts.adapter.ts)
- `AlertsDataAdapter` — generates alerts from mock data
- `AlertsRepository` — wraps localStorage read/write with the `alerts_v1` / `alert_audit_v1` keys
- Helper to generate alert ID, seed initial mock data, handle CSV export serialization

