### RBAC Layer

#### [NEW] [alerts-permissions.ts](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/lib/alerts-permissions.ts)
Exports:
- `getAlertPermissions(role)` → `{ canView, canConvert, canDismiss, canEscalate, viewScope }`
- `filterAlertsByRole(alerts, role, userDept?)` — enforces view scope
