### UI Components

#### [NEW] [AlertCard.tsx](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertCard.tsx)
- Vertical card with severity color strip (left border for LTR, right for RTL)
- Shows: title, employee/dept, risk%, trigger date, status badge
- Quick actions menu (⋮)
- Visual severity tints (critical=red, high=light-red, medium=amber, low=neutral)
- Selected/unread/hover states
- Checkbox for multi-select
- Hover mini-preview popover

#### [NEW] [AlertListPanel.tsx](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertListPanel.tsx)
- Scrollable list of `AlertCard` components
- Multi-select with shift+click range selection
- Selection state management
- Loading skeleton state
- Empty state

#### [NEW] [AlertDetailsPanel.tsx](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertDetailsPanel.tsx)
5 required sections using [TabsContainer](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/ui/navigation/TabsContainer.tsx#26-87):
1. **Summary** — ID, severity, status, triggered by, timestamp, assigned to, read indicator
2. **Signal Explanation (XAI)** — risk score, drivers, threshold, historical comparison
3. **Suggested Action** — recommendation, estimated impact, risk reduction
4. **Linked Entities** — employee profile link, department link, related cases
5. **Action Controls** — Acknowledge, Assign Owner, Convert to Case, Dismiss, Escalate
6. **Audit Trail** — immutable log of all state transitions

Also handles: loading, no-selection, error states. RBAC-aware button visibility.

#### [NEW] [AlertFilters.tsx](file:///d:/مشروع/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/features/alerts/AlertFilters.tsx)
Sticky filter bar:
- Severity filter (All/Critical/High/Medium/Low)
- Type filter (Attrition/Performance/Fairness/DataQuality/Threshold)
- Status filter (New/Acknowledged/Actioned/Closed/Archived)
- Date range
- Search (employee/department/alert ID)
- Toggle: Only Unread
- Sort: Newest/Highest Risk/Department
- Bulk action buttons: Mark All Read, Bulk Acknowledge, Bulk Convert, Export CSV

